:rgb(98,98,98)\">5</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:rgb(175,95,135)\">}</span><span style=\"color:rgb(175,0,0)\"> more)</span><span style=\"color:rgb(175,0,0)\">\"</span>\n<span class=\"ansi-green-fg\">--&gt; 200</span> <span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:rgb(0,135,0)\">raise</span> OutOfBoundsError(\n<span class=\"ansi-green-fg ansi-bold\">    201</span>     <span style=\"color:rgb(175,0,0)\">f</span><span style=\"color:rgb(175,0,0)\">\"</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:rgb(175,95,135)\">{</span>label<span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:rgb(175,95,135)\">}</span><span style=\"color:rgb(175,0,0)\"> out of bounds for spatial shape </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:rgb(175,95,135)\">{</span><span style=\"color:rgb(0,135,0)\">self</span><span style=\"color:rgb(98,98,98)\">.</span>_spatial_shape()<span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:rgb(175,95,135)\">}</span><span style=\"color:rgb(175,0,0)\">: </span><span style=\"color:rgb(175,0,0)\">\"</span>\n<span class=\"ansi-green-fg ansi-bold\">    202</span>     <span style=\"color:rgb(175,0,0)\">f</span><span style=\"color:rgb(175,0,0)\">\"</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:rgb(175,95,135)\">{</span>preview<span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:rgb(175,95,135)\">}</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:rgb(175,95,135)\">{</span>suffix<span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:rgb(175,95,135)\">}</span><span style=\"color:rgb(175,0,0)\">\"</span>\n<span class=\"ansi-green-fg ansi-bold\">    203</span> )\n\n<span class=\"ansi-red-fg\">OutOfBoundsError</span>: coordinate out of bounds for spatial shape (8, 8, 4): [[5004, 5004, 4002]]\n\nDuring handling of the above exception, another exception occurred:\n\n<span class=\"ansi-red-fg\">WorldOutOfBoundsError</span>                     Traceback (most recent call last)\nCell <span class=\"ansi-green-fg\">In[2], line 1</span>\n<span class=\"ansi-green-fg\">----&gt; 1</span> <span class=\"ansi-yellow-bg\">bold</span><span style=\"color:rgb(98,98,98)\